React Apps

React-specific apps made with Vite and Typescript. Each app is designed to be both pointer- and keyboard-accessible.

Dependencies:

  • react-icons
  • react-dom
  • react-router-dom
  • react-redux
  • @reduxjs/toolkit
  • axios
  • uuid

Dependencies (Node.js):

  • bcryptjs
  • cors
  • dotenv
  • express
  • express-validator
  • flatted
  • jsonwebtoken
  • mongoose
  • nodemailer
  • sanitize-html

  • Composer Olli Santa (Website)

    Olli Santa is a professional choir and orchestra conductor in the Southern Finland area. In addition to the artistic director's work, he composes and arranges music for all types of choirs, orchestras and bands.

  • Blob Art App

    Make blob art your thing. A custom draggables app with blobs that can be dragged around.

  • The Comedian's Companion

    A joke app with customizable options that uses the JokeAPI to fetch jokes. Submit a joke. See local jokes.

  • Quiz App

    A quiz app with three difficulty levels, a timer, and a highscore list. The app uses the The Trivia API to fetch questions.

  • Custom Select Dropdown

    A custom select component that can be used as a single- or multiple-select alternative.
